00:22:27.700 --> 00:22:34.960
<i>ashita wo shitte shimatta no ne</i>

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:39.500
<i>ikinasai saa</i>

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:39.500
Hadi, git

00:22:39.500 --> 00:22:44.210
<i>yakusoku no ie furi mukanaide</i>

00:22:39.500 --> 00:22:44.210
Vadedilmiş eve dönüp bakma

00:22:44.210 --> 00:22:48.930
<i>shinjinasai saa</i>

00:22:44.210 --> 00:22:48.930
İnan buna

00:22:48.930 --> 00:22:53.930
<i>afureru omoi tsuyosa ni kaete</i>

00:22:48.930 --> 00:22:53.930
Taşan duygularını güce dönüştür

00:22:53.930 --> 00:22:58.020
<i>kakemawaru anata no ashio to</i>

00:22:53.930 --> 00:22:58.020
